@host = http://localhost:5028

### Get Users v1
GET {{host}}/api/v1/users

### Get Users v2
GET {{host}}/api/v2/users

### Delete User (version-neutral)
DELETE {{host}}/api/users/1

### Get Scores v1
GET {{host}}/api/v1/scores

### Get Scores v2
GET {{host}}/api/v2/scores

### OpenAPI v1
GET {{host}}/openapi/v1.json

### OpenAPI v2
GET {{host}}/openapi/v2.json
